  <section>
    <h2>Vision Statement</h2>
    <p>“I believe the human mind is not just a place of thought, but the launchpad of destiny. I envision a world where distance is irrelevant, where thought unlocks movement, and where imagination becomes a legitimate force in reshaping reality.”</p>

    <h2>Core Idea</h2>
    <p><strong>Neuro-Triggered Instant Travel System (NTITS)</strong><br/>A theoretical system that enables instantaneous travel to real-world locations through focused thought, using brain-computer interfaces, quantum information transfer, and secure ethical AI protocols.</p>

    <h2>Purpose & Mission</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To push the limits of what is scientifically and ethically possible</li>
      <li>To pioneer a new frontier in human mobility and consciousness</li>
      <li>To ensure all technology serves the highest good of humanity</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Core Values</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Innovation with Integrity</li>
      <li>Human-Centered Progress</li>
      <li>Ethical Foresight</li>
      <li>Spiritual & Scientific Harmony</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Potential Benefits</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Eradicate barriers to access and opportunity</li>
      <li>Enable instant humanitarian aid and emergency relief</li>
      <li>Revolutionize transportation and sustainability</li>
      <li>Deepen human exploration and global connection</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Risks Acknowledged</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Invasion of bodily and cognitive privacy</li>
      <li>Weaponization or unethical use</li>
      <li>Existential and psychological challenges</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Ethical Framework</h2>
    <p>Establish a <strong>Global Council on Thought-Based Technologies</strong>, composed of ethicists, scientists, spiritual leaders, and futurists to govern, audit, and shape the development of thought-powered tech.</p>

    <h2>Long-Term Dream</h2>
    <p>To become a globally recognized thought leader in visionary science and ethical technology, ushering in a new age where thought is not just private—but transformational.</p>
